Wrangler — interactive DB-extraction (PI mode).

This tab is a login shell. Type `claude` to start the wrangler session.

The session reads the same database upstreams as the worker-facing wrangler
(from the project's role-mcps.json), so PI mode and worker mode see the same
DBs. Role + tools are auto-discovered when claude starts:

  /workspace/CLAUDE.md            the wrangler role prompt (symlink to role.md)
  /workspace/.tools-inventory.md  the live upstream / tool set

Publish finished artifacts to /workspace/published/ via `manifest describe`.
